{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/TIL/블로그를-만들기-까지.../","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Bee starter","author":"[Your Name]","siteUrl":"https://gatsby-starter-bee.netlify.com","comment":{"disqusShortName":"","utterances":"JaeYeopHan/gatsby-starter-bee"},"sponsor":{"buyMeACoffeeId":"jbee"}}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"21bb6a9b-6c5e-5bbc-9c99-3b857ef5bc88","excerpt":"오늘 드디어 블로그를 만들게 되었다.\n생각보다 많은 우여곡절이 있어서 첫번째 포스팅에 적어보려고한다.🚗🚓🚕 💦 템플릿 고르기 \n💦 배포방법 \n💦 permission denied? \n💦 github action   🚒 템플릿 고르기 Jekyll vs Gatsby 선택 장애가 있어 템플릿을 고를 때부터 머리가 아팠다.\n거두절미하고 Jekyll  와 Gatsby 가 최종 선택지였다. 결국 를 선택하게 되었다. SPA고 pc는 물론 mobile…","html":"<p>오늘 드디어 블로그를 만들게 되었다.<br>\n생각보다 많은 우여곡절이 있어서 첫번째 포스팅에 적어보려고한다.🚗🚓🚕</p>\n<p>💦 <a href=\"#template\">템플릿 고르기</a> <br>\n💦 <a href=\"#deploy\">배포방법</a> <br>\n💦 <a href=\"#denied\">permission denied?</a> <br>\n💦 <a href=\"#gitaction\">github action</a> <br></p>\n<p><span id=\"template\"></span></p>\n<h3 id=\"-템플릿-고르기-jekyll-vs-gatsby\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#-%ED%85%9C%ED%94%8C%EB%A6%BF-%EA%B3%A0%EB%A5%B4%EA%B8%B0-jekyll-vs-gatsby\" aria-label=\" 템플릿 고르기 jekyll vs gatsby permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>🚒 템플릿 고르기 Jekyll vs Gatsby</h3>\n<p>선택 장애가 있어 템플릿을 고를 때부터 머리가 아팠다.\n거두절미하고 Jekyll <code class=\"language-text\">minimal-mistakes</code> 와 Gatsby <code class=\"language-text\">gatsby-starter-bee</code>가 최종 선택지였다.</p>\n<p>결국 <code class=\"language-text\">gatsby-starter-bee</code>를 선택하게 되었다.</p>\n<p>SPA고 pc는 물론 mobile 반응형 화면까지 깔끔하다.\n그리고 배포도 간단해보였다.</p>\n<p><span id=\"deploy\"></span></p>\n<h3 id=\"-배포방법-publish-with-netlify-vs-github-pages\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#-%EB%B0%B0%ED%8F%AC%EB%B0%A9%EB%B2%95-publish-with-netlify-vs-github-pages\" aria-label=\" 배포방법 publish with netlify vs github pages permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>🚒 배포방법 Publish with netlify vs github pages</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/JaeYeopHan/gatsby-starter-bee#-gatsby-config\">gatsby-starter-bee</a> 에서 배포는 netlify와 github pages두가지 배포방법을 제시해놓았다.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://blog.outsider.ne.kr/1417\">netlify</a>는 서버 없이 쉽게 정적페이지를 배포해주는 도구라고한다.</p>\n<p>깃허브 페이지(GitHub Pages)는 깃허브에서 제공하는 정적 사이트 호스팅 서비스이다.</p>\n<p>나는 GitHub Pages를 통해 배포를 해보았다.</p>\n<p><span id=\"denied\"></span></p>\n<h3 id=\"-permission-denied\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#-permission-denied\" aria-label=\" permission denied permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>🚒 permission denied</h3>\n<p>gatsby-starter-bee에서는 github pages로 배포하는 방법을 아래 스크립트로 안내해줬다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token string\">\"scripts\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token string\">\"deploy\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"gatsby build &amp;&amp; gh-pages -d public -b master -r 'git@github.com:${your github id}/${github page name}.github.io.git'\"</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1058px; \">\n      <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 32.666666666666664%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(&apos;data:image/png;base64,&apos;); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" alt=\"error-img\" title=\"error-img\" src=\"/static/a41f1181dea2365d895ea251b29c8b56/bb2fd/blog-deploy-error.png\" srcset=\"/static/a41f1181dea2365d895ea251b29c8b56/5a46d/blog-deploy-error.png 300w,\n/static/a41f1181dea2365d895ea251b29c8b56/0a47e/blog-deploy-error.png 600w,\n/static/a41f1181dea2365d895ea251b29c8b56/bb2fd/blog-deploy-error.png 1058w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1058px) 100vw, 1058px\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\" loading=\"lazy\">\n    </span>\n<br>\n하지만... 계속 permission denied 이라고 떴다.\n<br>\n결국 git action으로 github pages를 배포하게 되었다.\n<span id=\"gitaction\"></span>\n<h3 id=\"-github-action으로-gh-pages-배포하기\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#-github-action%EC%9C%BC%EB%A1%9C-gh-pages-%EB%B0%B0%ED%8F%AC%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0\" aria-label=\" github action으로 gh pages 배포하기 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>🚒 github action으로 gh-pages 배포하기</h3>\n<p>최근에 git action을 통해 배포한 경험이 있어서 git action을 통해 github pages를 배포하기로 했다.<br><br>\nmain 브런치에는 기존 폴더들이, public 폴더에 있는 빌드된 파일들이 gh-pages 브런치에 배포되도록 했다.</p>\n<p>✔ main 브런치가 push 될 때 git action이 실행되도록 했다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"yml\"><pre class=\"language-yml\"><code class=\"language-yml\"><span class=\"token key atrule\">on</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n  <span class=\"token key atrule\">push</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n    <span class=\"token key atrule\">branches</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">-</span> main</code></pre></div>\n<p>✔ 기본 root를 gh-pages브런치로 설정 해놔야 한다.\n<span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 704px; \">\n      <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 42%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(&apos;data:image/png;base64,&apos;); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" alt=\"gh-pages-img\" title=\"gh-pages-img\" src=\"/static/6921d8a486ec3df8ef3444d9159b00c0/5ebd7/gh-pages.png\" srcset=\"/static/6921d8a486ec3df8ef3444d9159b00c0/5a46d/gh-pages.png 300w,\n/static/6921d8a486ec3df8ef3444d9159b00c0/0a47e/gh-pages.png 600w,\n/static/6921d8a486ec3df8ef3444d9159b00c0/5ebd7/gh-pages.png 704w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 704px) 100vw, 704px\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\" loading=\"lazy\">\n    </span></p>\n<p>✔ <a href=\"https://github.com/peaceiris/actions-gh-pages\">gitflows 참고 사항은 여기에!</a></p>","frontmatter":{"title":"EP.1 블로그를 만들기 까지...","date":"November 05, 2020"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/TIL/블로그를-만들기-까지.../","previous":null,"next":null}},"staticQueryHashes":["3128451518","521680639"]}